00079 #ifndef __glew_h__
00080 #define __glew_h__
00081 #define __GLEW_H__
00082 
00083 #if defined(__gl_h_) || defined(__GL_H__) || defined(__X_GL_H)
00084 #error gl.h included before glew.h
00085 #endif
00086 #if defined(__glext_h_) || defined(__GLEXT_H_)
00087 #error glext.h included before glew.h
00088 #endif
00089 #if defined(__gl_ATI_h_)
00090 #error glATI.h included before glew.h
00091 #endif
00092 
00093 // **Modified** Added `#define GLEW_STATIC` for internal build into a static lib
00094 #define GLEW_STATIC
00095 
00096 #define __gl_h_
00097 #define __GL_H__
00098 #define __X_GL_H
00099 #define __glext_h_
00100 #define __GLEXT_H_
00101 #define __gl_ATI_h_
00102 
00103 #if defined(_WIN32)
00104 
00105 /*
00106  * GLEW does not include <windows.h> to avoid name space pollution.
00107  * GL needs GLAPI and GLAPIENTRY, GLU needs APIENTRY, CALLBACK, and wchar_t
00108  * defined properly.
00109  */
00110 /* <windef.h> */
00111 #ifndef APIENTRY
00112 #define GLEW_APIENTRY_DEFINED
00113 #  if defined(__MINGW32__) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
00114 #    define APIENTRY __stdcall
00115 #  elif (_MSC_VER >= 800) || defined(_STDCALL_SUPPORTED) || defined(__BORLANDC__)
00116 #    define APIENTRY __stdcall
00117 #  else
00118 #    define APIENTRY
00119 #  endif
00120 #endif
00121 #ifndef GLAPI
00122 #  if defined(__MINGW32__) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
00123 #    define GLAPI extern
00124 #  endif
00125 #endif
00126 /* <winnt.h> */
00127 #ifndef CALLBACK
00128 #define GLEW_CALLBACK_DEFINED
00129 #  if defined(__MINGW32__) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
00130 #    define CALLBACK __attribute__ ((__stdcall__))
00131 #  elif (defined(_M_MRX000) || defined(_M_IX86) || defined(_M_ALPHA) || defined(_M_PPC)) && !defined(MIDL_PASS)
00132 #    define CALLBACK __stdcall
00133 #  else
00134 #    define CALLBACK
00135 #  endif
00136 #endif
00137 /* <wingdi.h> and <winnt.h> */
00138 #ifndef WINGDIAPI
00139 #define GLEW_WINGDIAPI_DEFINED
00140 #define WINGDIAPI __declspec(dllimport)
00141 #endif
00142 /* <ctype.h> */
00143 #if (defined(_MSC_VER) || defined(__BORLANDC__)) && !defined(_WCHAR_T_DEFINED)
00144 typedef unsigned short wchar_t;
00145 #  define _WCHAR_T_DEFINED
00146 #endif
00147 /* <stddef.h> */
00148 #if !defined(_W64)
00149 #  if !defined(__midl) && (defined(_X86_) || defined(_M_IX86)) && defined(_MSC_VER) && _MSC_VER >= 1300
00150 #    define _W64 __w64
00151 #  else
00152 #    define _W64
00153 #  endif
00154 #endif
00155 #if !defined(_PTRDIFF_T_DEFINED) && !defined(_PTRDIFF_T_) && !defined(__MINGW64__)
00156 #  ifdef _WIN64
00157 typedef __int64 ptrdiff_t;
00158 #  else
00159 typedef _W64 int ptrdiff_t;
00160 #  endif
00161 #  define _PTRDIFF_T_DEFINED
00162 #  define _PTRDIFF_T_
00163 #endif
00164 
00165 #ifndef GLAPI
00166 #  if defined(__MINGW32__) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
00167 #    define GLAPI extern
00168 #  else
00169 #    define GLAPI WINGDIAPI
00170 #  endif
00171 #endif
00172 
00173 #ifndef GLAPIENTRY
00174 #define GLAPIENTRY APIENTRY
00175 #endif
00176 
00177 /*
00178  * GLEW_STATIC is defined for static library.
00179  * GLEW_BUILD  is defined for building the DLL library.
00180  */
00181 
00182 #ifdef GLEW_STATIC
00183 #  define GLEWAPI extern
00184 #else
00185 #  ifdef GLEW_BUILD
00186 #    define GLEWAPI extern __declspec(dllexport)
00187 #  else
00188 #    define GLEWAPI extern __declspec(dllimport)
00189 #  endif
00190 #endif
00191 
00192 #else /* _UNIX */
00193 
00194 /*
00195  * Needed for ptrdiff_t in turn needed by VBO.  This is defined by ISO
00196  * C.  On my system, this amounts to _3 lines_ of included code, all of
00197  * them pretty much harmless.  If you know of a way of detecting 32 vs
00198  * 64 _targets_ at compile time you are free to replace this with
00199  * something that's portable.  For now, _this_ is the portable solution.
00200  * (mem, 2004-01-04)
00201  */
00202 
00203 #include <stddef.h>
00204 
00205 /* SGI MIPSPro doesn't like stdint.h in C++ mode */
00206 
00207 #if defined(__sgi) && !defined(__GNUC__)
00208 #include <inttypes.h>
00209 #else
00210 #include <stdint.h>
00211 #endif
00212 
00213 #define GLEW_APIENTRY_DEFINED
00214 #define APIENTRY
00215 
00216 /*
00217  * GLEW_STATIC is defined for static library.
00218  */
00219 
00220 #ifdef GLEW_STATIC
00221 #  define GLEWAPI extern
00222 #else
00223 #  if defined(__GNUC__) && __GNUC__>=4
00224 #   define GLEWAPI extern __attribute__ ((visibility("default")))
00225 #  elif defined(__SUNPRO_C) || defined(__SUNPRO_CC)
00226 #   define GLEWAPI extern __global
00227 #  else
00228 #   define GLEWAPI extern
00229 #  endif
00230 #endif

00233 #ifndef GLAPI
00234 #define GLAPI extern
00235 #endif
00236 #ifndef GLAPIENTRY
00237 #define GLAPIENTRY
00238 #endif
00239 
00240 #endif /* _WIN32 */
